Package: RCMEMS
Type: Package
Title: R interface to the Copernicus Marine Environment Monitoring Service (CMEMS)
Version: 1.0
Author: Mark R. Payne [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5795-2481>)
Maintainer: Mark R. Payne <mpay@aqua.dtu.dk> 
Description: Provides an R-friendly wrapper around the Python-based motuclient that
    can be used to download and subset data directly from the Copernicus Marine 
    Environmental Monitoring Service (CMEMS) data stores (<http://marine.copernicus.eu>).
URL: https://github.com/markpayneatwork/RCMEMS
BugReports: https://github.com/markpayneatwork/RCMEMS/issues
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyData: TRUE
Imports: methods
Suggests:
    raster,
    xml2,
    testthat (>= 2.1.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
Encoding: UTF-8
